      <title>MoneyGram 贷款重新定价在早期交易困难后完成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/moneygram-s-loan-repricing-completed-after-early-deal-struggles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于评级较低的公司纷纷降低借贷成本，而投资者对高息债务的渴求，速汇金国际公司 (MoneyGram International Inc.) 上周在提高报价条件后，完成了 3.98 亿美元杠杆贷款的重新定价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/moneygram-s-loan-repricing-completed-after-early-deal-struggles</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 19:38:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际纸业寻求安抚 DS，因为 Suzano 正在策划竞标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/international-paper-seeks-to-reassure-ds-as-suzano-plots-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，国际纸业公司高管前往伦敦重申公司对合并伙伴 DS Smith Plc 的承诺，并淡化了 Suzano SA 的收购要约，该收购要约可能会破坏双方即将达成的价值 58 亿英镑（74 亿美元）的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/international-paper-seeks-to-reassure-ds-as-suzano-plots-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 18:41:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
